# .gitignore for Visual Studio / .NET projects

## Build output
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]64/
[Bb]uild/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/

## Visual Studio user-specific files
.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.userprefs

## Rider / JetBrains
.idea/

## VS Code
.vscode/

## NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
**/packages/*
!**/packages/build/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

## .NET / MSBuild
*.dll
*.pdb
*.exe
!**/lib/**/*.dll
TestResults/
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## Visual Studio upgrade/migration reports
UpgradeLog*.htm
_UpgradeReport_Files/
Backup*/

## OS files
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
.DS_Store

## App-specific (later phases may add user config we don't want committed)
# settings.local.json
